 Dakore Egbuson-Akande,  Oris Erhuero and Nse Ikpe Etim during the premiere in Victoria Island, Lagos. Truly, the course of true love never did run smooth, as some even described love as a devil. Nonetheless, there is no evil angel but Love. Who will survive the ‘devil’s’ antics between Toyin and her childhood friend, Uche in A Sunday Affair? 